const metadata$24 = { "headers": [{ "depth": 2, "slug": "1-jamie-foxx-roasting-doug-williams", "text": "1. Jamie Foxx roasting Doug Williams" }, { "depth": 2, "slug": "2-princes-while-my-guitar-gently-weeps-guitar-solo-but-with-more-prince\uFE0F", "text": "2. Prince\u2019s While My Guitar Gently weeps guitar solo, but with More Prince\u2122\uFE0F" }, { "depth": 2, "slug": "3-clips-of-star-trek", "text": "3. Clips of Star Trek" }, { "depth": 2, "slug": "4-aaron-cybertron-zheng", "text": "4. Aaron \u2018Cybertron\u2019 Zheng" }, { "depth": 2, "slug": "5-khruangbin", "text": "5. Khruangbin" }], "source": "\nIt's tough out there (or should that be in here?) and because I don't watch TV, I take comfort in YouTube when I need some visual stimulation. Here are some videos I've been watching to keep my mind off things. Might make this into a series.\n\n## 1. Jamie Foxx roasting Doug Williams\n\n[plugin:youtube](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tq2ivETREGo)\n\nIt's old but I found this again via another video and it's been good to revisit this hilarious meta-roast and get some laughs.\n\n## 2. Prince's While My Guitar Gently weeps guitar solo, but with More Prince\u2122\uFE0F\n\n[plugin:youtube](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CdfMh8QgJjA)\n\nAnother classic I regularly watch but this new version has more close ups of Prince and my goodness, it's even better. I actually welled up today watching it. Breathtaking.\n\n(The \u2122\uFE0F thing is a meme; please don't sue, The Purple One's Lawyers!)\n\n## 3. Clips of Star Trek\n\n[plugin:youtube](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FggqbNUZD8U)\n\nMost of them have been of The Next Generation but Deep Space 9 will always be my #1. This clips shows Elim Garak giving zero fucks about Gul Dukat's feelings and I love him for it.\n\n## 4. Aaron 'Cybertron' Zheng\n\n[plugin:youtube](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=adVF6bcyZjc)\n\nAs I continue to get into Pok\xE9mon VGC, I keep watching Aaron 'Cybertron' Zheng's awesome videos for inspiration, tips, and the love of Pok\xE9mon. He's one of the greatest VGC players of all time and if you're into VGC, you need to subscribe.\n\n## 5. Khruangbin\n\n[plugin:youtube](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vsSmzapbKv4)\n\nJust listen. And find more of their music and listen some more. They're my pick for best band out right now and that'll be the happiest hill I'll ever die on.\n", "html": '<p>It\u2019s tough out there (or should that be in here?) and because I don\u2019t watch TV, I take comfort in YouTube when I need some visual stimulation. Here are some videos I\u2019ve been watching to keep my mind off things. Might make this into a series.</p>\n<h2 id="1-jamie-foxx-roasting-doug-williams">1. Jamie Foxx roasting Doug Williams</h2>\n<p><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tq2ivETREGo">plugin:youtube</a></p>\n<p>It\u2019s old but I found this again via another video and it\u2019s been good to revisit this hilarious meta-roast and get some laughs.</p>\n<h2 id="2-princes-while-my-guitar-gently-weeps-guitar-solo-but-with-more-prince\uFE0F">2. Prince\u2019s While My Guitar Gently weeps guitar solo, but with More Prince\u2122\uFE0F</h2>\n<p><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CdfMh8QgJjA">plugin:youtube</a></p>\n<p>Another classic I regularly watch but this new version has more close ups of Prince and my goodness, it\u2019s even better. I actually welled up today watching it. Breathtaking.</p>\n<p>(The \u2122\uFE0F thing is a meme; please don\u2019t sue, The Purple One\u2019s Lawyers!)</p>\n<h2 id="3-clips-of-star-trek">3. Clips of Star Trek</h2>\n<p><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FggqbNUZD8U">plugin:youtube</a></p>\n<p>Most of them have been of The Next Generation but Deep Space 9 will always be my #1. This clips shows Elim Garak giving zero fucks about Gul Dukat\u2019s feelings and I love him for it.</p>\n<h2 id="4-aaron-cybertron-zheng">4. Aaron \u2018Cybertron\u2019 Zheng</h2>\n<p><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=adVF6bcyZjc">plugin:youtube</a></p>\n<p>As I continue to get into Pok\xE9mon VGC, I keep watching Aaron \u2018Cybertron\u2019 Zheng\u2019s awesome videos for inspiration, tips, and the love of Pok\xE9mon. He\u2019s one of the greatest VGC players of all time and if you\u2019re into VGC, you need to subscribe.</p>\n<h2 id="5-khruangbin">5. Khruangbin</h2>\n<p><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vsSmzapbKv4">plugin:youtube</a></p>\n<p>Just listen. And find more of their music and listen some more. They\u2019re my pick for best band out right now and that\u2019ll be the happiest hill I\u2019ll ever die on.</p>' };
